&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Build and standardize scalable operational processes across data collection sites, warehouses, and annotation workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Drive process excellence initiatives focused on quality, efficiency, throughput, and operational reliability&lt;/li&gt;
