&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an R&amp;amp;D Assembly Technician to join our hardware team and play a hands-on role in building and bringing up early prototype units. You&#39;ll work closely with mechanical, electrical, and manufacturing engineers to assemble, wire, and calibrate new systems and feed your firsthand build experience back into the designs.&lt;/p&gt;
